cetus.transforms

Class EventTimer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.transforms.TransformPass
      • cetus.transforms.EventTimer

  • public class EventTimer
extends TransformPass
    This pass instruments the program that contains PragmaAnnotation.Event annotations. The annotations may be inserted either manually or automatically.
